{"title_page": "1936\u201337 Slovenian Republic League", "text_new": "{{Use dmy dates|date=August 2013}}\n{{Infobox football league season\n| competition = [[Slovenian Republic League]]\n| season = 1936\u201337\n| winners = [[NK \u017delezni\u010dar Maribor|\u017delezni\u010dar Maribor]]\n| total goals = 302\n| prevseason = [[1935\u201336 Slovenian Republic League|1935\u201336]]\n| nextseason = [[1937\u201338 Slovenian Republic League|1937\u201338]]\n}}\nThe '''1936\u201337 Slovenian Republic League''' was the 18th season of the [[Slovenian Republic Football League|Slovenian Republic League]]. [[NK \u017delezni\u010dar Maribor|\u017delezni\u010dar Maribor]] have won the league for the first time.<ref name=\"league\">{{cite web | url = http://www.mnzveza-mb.si/datoteke/e-katalog/index.html | title = MNZ Maribor - 80 let nogometa v Mariboru |trans-title=80 years of football in Maribor| publisher = MNZ Maribor | year = 2008 | accessdate = 14 August 2013 | language = Slovenian }}</ref>\n\n==Ljubljana subdivision==\n{{#invoke:sports table|main|style=WDL\n|res_col_header=Q\n|sortable_table=y\n|winpoints=2\n\n|team1=AMA|name_AMA=[[SK Amater|Amater]]\n|team2=OLI|name_OLI=[[NK Olimp Celje|Olimp]]\n|team3=KRA|name_KRA=[[NK Triglav Kranj (defunct)|Kranj]]\n|team4=SLO|name_SLO=[[ND Slovan|Slovan]]\n|team5=HER|name_HER=[[\u017dSK Hermes|Hermes]]\n|team6=REK|name_REK=[[SK Reka|Reka]]\n|win_AMA=5|draw_AMA=2|loss_AMA=3|gf_AMA=17|ga_AMA=16\n|win_OLI=3|draw_OLI=5|loss_OLI=2|gf_OLI=17|ga_OLI=18\n|win_KRA=4|draw_KRA=2|loss_KRA=4|gf_KRA=24|ga_KRA=18\n|win_SLO=4|draw_SLO=2|loss_SLO=4|gf_SLO=20|ga_SLO=20\n|win_HER=4|draw_HER=1|loss_HER=5|gf_HER=14|ga_HER=20\n|win_REK=3|draw_REK=2|loss_REK=5|gf_REK=18|ga_REK=18\n\n|col_C=green1|text_C=\n|result1=C|result2=C\n|update=complete|source=\n}}\n\n==Maribor subdivision==\n{{#invoke:sports table|main|style=WDL\n|res_col_header=Q\n|sortable_table=y\n|winpoints=2\n\n|team1=MRB|name_MRB=[[NK \u017delezni\u010dar Maribor|\u017delezni\u010dar Maribor]]\